        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得走石飞砂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "那一旁坐定了观音菩萨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "昏沉沉也不知落在谁家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "猛然间睁开眼太湖石下"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "适才间奴投澜一心无假"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不是妖魔鬼怪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "本非是妖魔怪休要惊怕，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不是妖魔鬼怪，你是甚等样人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "奴本是落难人奔走天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听你之言，你是被难之人，意欲带你去见我家母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭小姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "她本是落难人来到我家，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由我一阵阵心内如麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（邹母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的儿请为娘有何根芽？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀母亲：孩儿花园游玩，得一难女，母亲请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是一被难之人，叫她前来见我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难女前来见过母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈杏元 （旦） 叩见老夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一难女因何到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老夫人问我的真情实话，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "泄机关又恐怕被人所杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "陈杏元改换了汪月英，哄骗与她。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由人一霎时为难心下"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一女子，为何背地沉吟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难女怎敢背地沉吟。夫人、小姐请高坐，听难女一言告禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊夫人与小姐听奴言讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "细听我落难人叙说端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奴姓汪名月英父母在堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨卢杞命杏元去和番邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "选美女四十名一同——"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "前往，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有小女在其内离了故乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奴投在落雁坡一命身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又谁知落在了夫人花墙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊夫人、贤小姐听奴言讲："
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奴情愿为使女又待何妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家住在扬州郡江都小县"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都只为雁门关打了败仗"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到他国不过是下贱之样"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒙神圣保佑我性命未丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听伊言来泪悲伤，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "骂声卢杞狗奸党！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哭板） 只害得他一家人东逃西往，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝母亲免悲泪慈悲心肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，母亲，我看此女，生的倒也聪明伶俐，何不将她收留府下，做一位螟蛉义"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女，母亲意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一难女，可知我们是甚等样人家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难女不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家老爷现任河南八府巡按，老身受过诰命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是一名诰命夫人，小女子不知，多多有罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身有意将你收留府下，做一位螟蛉义女，不知你意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还不前来拜见母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，母亲请上，受孩儿一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "喜洋洋近前来双膝跪倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声老夫人细听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到后来儿不忘教养恩高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在府中望母亲多多训教"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知你叫何名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫汪月英。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。改姓不改名，改为邹月英。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢母亲起名，但不知小姐青春几何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一十六岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家二九，占长了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长则长，幼则幼，二人在这绣楼前，当着老身一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫姐姐你请上受我一拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与你好一比一母同胎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐请上，受愚姐一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "近前来把贤妹一生高叫，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为姐的有一言细听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "咱二人犹如那一母同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在府中早晚间多多看照"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫丫鬟将酒宴后堂摆好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母女们饮一个快乐逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（邹母下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫姐姐休得要珠泪嚎啕，"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与你好一似一母同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒙夫人与小姐恩高义好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日里在邹府独自逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邹云英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "背转思贤公子珠泪垂掉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈杏元",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的梅……"
